title: Double Trouble 2022: Lions & Vikings
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp tackle a Double Trouble on the Lions and Vikings, including if D'Andre Swift is a Top 5 RB this year and how early you should draft Justin Jefferson. Then, they dive into some key notes for your drafts.
